      • PnController

        public PnController(java.util.LinkedList<SolenoidBoth> solenoids,
                    java.util.LinkedList<edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.Compressor> compressors)
        Constuctor for the pneumatics control. It would be advisable to add the solenoids to the list in a way that corresponds to their PCM value, same with the compressor.
        Parameters:
        solenoids - a list of all solenoids currently on the system.
        compressors - a list of all compressors currently on the system.
